                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-31-off167 t18190915-31-cd168"></join>, one pocket-handkerchief, value 2 s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190915-31-victim314" type="victimName">
                           William 
